We want to share this pictures not only because we are celebrating 13 years since we said yes to each other but also to inspire other couples that might be going through problems, Even though many people told us we were too young to get married and that we wouldn’t last not even a year, by the mercy of God we’re still together and celebrating our love. Just like many marriages we been through a lot of tribulations but who said it was going to be easy? love will always defeat. The 4 most common causes of divorce are lack of commitment, infidelity, too much conflict and arguing, and lack of physical intimacy. There is no such thing as a perfect relationship so don’t be fooled by what you see on social media but if you put God in the center of your marriage he will protect it. #happyanniversary
